{"tid":1270393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我好想同每一個屋企人講","createTime":"2019-06-30T23:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T23:26:37.000Z","uid":104390,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bde5bd5f0628fccacaabaa32a7ae49145f37b2a1","tid":1270393,"uid":104390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T23:03:44.000Z","msg":"2014年之後一直有道疤痕留左係香港人心入面，差唔多五年時間過去左，但哩道疤痕好似仲未係每個人心入面消散，然而哩個六月又增多一道新嘅疤痕，香港人大家好攰，但我想講，香港人只少係我心入係哩個世界上最善良最美嘅民族，香港人呀，大家一定要撐住呀，我地大家嘅屋企靠曬我地咁多人一齊黎守護架啦，我唔想哩個屋企再有一個屋企人離開我地，有咩事咪同其他屋企人傾下囉，我地一家人黎架嗎係咪，如果再有屋企人走，哩個屋企就撐唔住架啦，咁多位屋企人撐住，應承我啦唔好再離開屋企好唔好，我都就黎頂唔順，但我地一齊努力好唔好，哩個屋企少緊一個都唔叫一個屋企，一家人齊齊極極先叫一家人架嗎，我地一家人一齊再努力啦好唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最愛大家嘅屋企人上<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f031d1d17070410f7c37f14791c9e2636efa20ec","tid":1270393,"uid":128590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T23:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a94d34933caafcfe186cb2b8afe4d2f49297d7","tid":1270393,"uid":104390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f031d1d17070410f7c37f14791c9e2636e