d34933caafcfe186cb2b8afe4d2f49297d7","tid":1270393,"uid":104390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f031d1d17070410f7c37f14791c9e2636efa20ec","tid":1270393,"uid":128590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T23:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T23:08:45.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄，我由69一直喊到今日，大家屋企有咩就講比大家聽啦，唔好屈住屈住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我⋯⋯以家唔係香港<br />\n好撚難受<br />\n發夢一直係前線<br />\n但以家逼住走咗<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好咁講啦，要你一直發啲咁嘅夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我作為一個香港人無發到啲上前線嘅望我自己都好內疚，哩二個星期我自己嘅情緒都崩潰左，日日一開電腦就喊，我琴日都要搵社工做情緒輔導。<br />\n我知每一個屋企人都好難受，個個日日都發惡夢，日日都聽到好多惡嘅消息，但我想講我地一家人黎架嗎，有咩咪講出黎，大家共同進退，齊上齊落。<br />\n真係攰嘅話就出去抖下啦，抖到夠啦先返黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地會係屋企等你返黎架啦，最緊要你要完完整整無事咁返黎大家身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好怪自已啦，大家屋企人會努力幫手撐住架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應承我，好好咁休息一下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7145b6bf34fee54215ce14910269d462fd69524f","tid":1270393,"uid":128590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6970a7e23e4852b4ced7d545c8b2962b264dce80","tid":1270393,"uid":104390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6475656d6e54edcf567b5cd2e11eb10a8a273f04","tid":1270393,"uid":128590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92a94d34933caafcfe186cb2b8afe4d2f49297d7","tid":1270393,"uid":104390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T23:08:45.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄，我由69一直喊到今日，大家屋企有咩就講比大家聽啦，唔好屈住屈住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我⋯⋯以家唔係香港<br />\n好撚難受<br />\n發夢一直係前線<br />\n但以家逼住走咗<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj